reviews.text: Lunch walk-in at 1230, on a weekday. Pretty good service, fast delivery of food. Average food.
Good food but extremely poor service(waitress)

It’s a relative score (4 stars) based on what this place is. It’s a quick fast food formulaic Japanese place and for lunch sets. Reasonably priced between 68-100+ dollars for lunch sets.  If your expecting amazing Japanese food then you’re really not able to figure out restaurant types but if you a smart enough to know this place is fast-casual (think chipotle) then the 4 stars is our surprise at the amount we enjoyed the food.

It was good basic food, perhaps overly msg/salty but cheap and cheerful and we walked away surprisingly satisfied.
Fried chickens tastes like microwave reheated.    Mushrooms are rotten.   Luckily I didn't order sashimi or sushi.
Matcha Sapporo beer must try!

星期五晚7:00不用等位，直入，吧枱位。
服務一般喇，要換碟唔識，反而排住收碟，埋單唔爭在客人走先收野，唔該。食物，刺身都算新鮮，但似乎千両稍勝。燒物合格，可再整熱些。燒餅也是可熱些。吞拿魚溶壽司不錯。
這間日本餐廳的食物都ok 價錢在v city裏面比較貴些少其實都合理因為租金都會幾貴

非常滿意
食物質素相當高、價錢中上、環境闊落……繁忙時段需稍等才端上食物，食物賣相相當精緻，份量雖算多、但也會再次光顧。

首先，服務態度一流，由門口介紹到侍應，都好有熱誠。
其次，食物都有水準，套餐都有物超所值感覺。
美中不足係個特飲，太甜太藥水味，只好慶幸自己事先叫左梅酒飲
環境舒適，食物質素唔錯，今次係套餐另加多個黑豚燒炒麵。可能迎合香港環境同埋響商場裏面，冇左響日本果種既大排檔居酒屋感覺。各有各好，香港呢間勝在企理乾淨，坐得舒服，價錢可以接受。

reviews.text: Clean and new shopping mall. Huge supermarket yata on top floor. Also some amazing restaurants
Good mall for medium brands shopping. Good varieties of restaurants and food court available. Ample parking space.
High end shopping centre with high end prices. Food court here is really good and has plenty of variety. Even if your budget don't reach that far come for the spotless toilets and air conditioning.
Great mall, nice, clean and big. Was attached to our hotel so very convenient for shopping, getting a coffee and dinner. Recommended.
Huge mall. Fantastic variety of shops.. many restaurants to choose from..in the same complex as our motel. Easy to navigate. Very popular.
